- `SECURE_SSL_REDIRECT` — All HTTP requests redirected to HTTPS
- `SECURE_HSTS_*` — Tells browsers to *always* use HTTPS for your domain for 1 year
- `X_FRAME_OPTIONS = 'DENY'` — Prevents your site from being loaded in an iframe (clickjacking protection)

**Why wrapped in `if not DEBUG`?** These settings require HTTPS. In development you use HTTP, so enabling them would break your local server.

