## Production Checklist

Before deploying to production, make sure:

- [ ] `DEBUG=False` in `.env`
- [ ] `SECRET_KEY` is a randomly generated 50+ character string
- [ ] `ALLOWED_HOSTS` contains only your actual domain
- [ ] MySQL user has limited privileges (not root)
- [ ] Email is configured with a production email service
- [ ] HTTPS is configured (SSL certificate)
- [ ] Static files are served via nginx/CDN, not Django
- [ ] `python manage.py check --deploy` passes all checks
- [ ] Rate limiting is tuned for your expected traffic

